-----------------------------

drivers are maintained as accounts in epbcs

driver accounts:
sales_volume
unit_price
growth_rate
inflation_%
headcount
salary_rate
energy_kwh
depreciation rate

drivers are non transactional accounts of type non financial or statistical

***  drivers can also be maintained as smart lists ( categorical drivers ) --> attribute dmns ??

how drivers are entered ??

entered in planning forms just like normal account input
drivers are always input accounts of store type, they will not be dynamic calc in general

volume and price are inputed by financial users and revenue is generated by calculations
